The Pacific Links Golf Network

A global reciprocal program, offering valuable benefits to participating clubs and their members.

Our goal is to connect international golfers and world-class golf destinations to take your membership to the next level.

Explore the Network
Bear Mountain Resort, Victoria, BC, Canada

The Network is...

Royal Hawaiian Golf Club, Oahu, Hawaii

Versatile

Joining the network means tapping into new markets. You can retain members, attract new ones and fill open tee times.

Red Mountain Golf Club, Phuket, Thailand

Reciprocal

Members of each Network Club enjoy special rates at all participating clubs.

Sueno Golf Club, Belek, Turkey

Accessible

Requesting tee times is simple for everyone. All requests go through our in-house booking system.

What drives you?

Dragon Ridge Country Club, Nevada, USA
The Scandinavian Golf Club, Denmark
Blackhawk Golf Club, Alberta, Canada
Woodlands Golf Club, Australia
Previous Next

Spoil your members.

Pacific Links Affiliate Clubs are part of a select group of network clubs that are focused on giving their members a truly valuable golf travel benefit. These clubs recognize how a rich global membership benefit differentiates them in their locally market.

100+

Affiliate Clubs

21

Countries Represented

250+

Reciprocal Clubs

26

Countries Represented

Global golf is coming.

Pacific Links Reciprocal Clubs are engaged and ready to take on our Network Golfers. If you are looking to fill tee times, this is where you belong.

16,000+

Pacific Links
International Members

125,000+

Network Golfers

18,900

Rounds Delivered in 2018

350+

Network Clubs

Explore the Network

Members of Affiliate Clubs are entitled to complimentary greens fees at other Affiliate Clubs and to a significant discount off published greens fees at Reciprocal Clubs.

Members of Reciprocal Clubs are entitled to a significant discount off published greens fees at both Affiliate and Reciprocal Clubs.

We are THE portal to the traveling Chinese golfer.

Pacific Links sells an elite membership product in East Asia and now services 16,000 + members. Our travel department delivered over 7,000 rounds to our Network Clubs who were seeking this business in 2018 and is always on the lookout for the next iconic destination to market to our members.

Angkor Golf Resort, Cambodia
Laguna National Golf & Country Club, Singapore
Vinpearl Golf Nha Trang, Nha Trang, Vietnam

We respect your turf

We respect and protect the traditions of your club. Members of participating clubs may use their Pacific Links privileges at clubs that are more than 150 kilometers away from their home club or residence(s).

We respect your tee sheet

Your tee sheet will always be under your control. Your members still come first. There is no need to block out tee times for the Network.

We respect your members

There’s no need to worry about large groups. Network privileges are provided to independent travelers. Bookings with over 8 players are subject to a different rate applied to individuals in that group and subject to acceptance by the club.

No cost to join.

That’s right. There is no cost to join. We will not charge your club nor your members anything to participate and we take no commissions on tee times. Our primary business is selling an elite membership product in East Asia called the Pacific Links International membership.

Pacific Links International Members receive similar benefits to members of Network Clubs, so having a diverse and extensive list of Affiliate and Reciprocal Clubs enhances the marketability of our product while giving your club worldwide exposure.

Our foremost commitment is to our Network Clubs who make this all possible.

Learn more

By providing us your email address, you are consenting to receive electronic Network Golfer updates from Pacific Links International.
